SELECT "user_auth_tokens".* FROM "user_auth_tokens" WHERE ((auth_token = 'wttADILeU+ZDA7mjXTosb6j5hBc=' OR
                          prev_auth_token = 'wttADILeU+ZDA7mjXTosb6j5hBc=') AND rotated_at > '2020-03-29 18:56:04.131162') LIMIT 1
